perl allows both trailing commas and also optional list-quoting which breaks on whitespace (commas unneeded):<p><pre><code>    my @stuff = (
      "foo",
      "bar",
      "baz",
    );
</code></pre>
or:<p><pre><code>    my @stuff = qw(
      foo
      bar
      baz
    );
</code></pre>
or<p><pre><code>  my @stuff = qw(foo bar baz);
</code></pre>
TIMTOWDI indeed...
